gText_Host_Welcome::
	.string "Hi! Sorry to keep you waiting!\p"
	.string "Welcome to Survival Island!\n"
	.string "I am DONATHAN, your host.\p"
	.string "Survival Island is a timed-”\n"
	.string "attack survival-based game\l"
	.string "involving POKéMON and trainers.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Host_Pokemon::
	.string "As you are probably aware, this\n"
	.string "is a POKéMON.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Host_MainSpeech::
	.string "Survival island is a tough\n"
	.string "challenge that tests a trainers\l"
	.string "mettle and knowledge in POKéMON.\p"
	.string "It is not for the faint hearted.\n"
	.string "You, as a trainer, are tasked with\l"
	.string "reaching the end of the island,\l"
	.string "battling trainers along the way,\l"
	.string "aided by the POKéMON you have\l"
	.string "captured.\p"
	.string "It is a difficult task, but you\n"
	.string "will have the help of items and\l"
	.string "materials along the way.\p"
	.string "I hope you are up to the\n"
	.string "challenge!\p"
	.string "$"

